::Iron Raptor/Prowl/Cledar/Rixer/Forrior/Blyer/Forrior::

Iron Raptor looks around at the Maximals, her gaze pausing on the talking group. She then looks back at the four new Maximals after inspecting her troops.

"Ok, fall in. We'll begin shortly."

Iron Raptor walks over to a console and begins to type up the simulation that the Maximals will be training in.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl, Cledar, Rixer, Forrior, Blyer, and Firearm stand at attention, patiently waiting.
